What you need to know:

The 46-year-old Tangatanga lawmaker is set to marry her long-term political partner, turned sweetheart, businessman Samuel Mburu.DP Ruto, who led Mr Mburu's side in the dowry negotiations, said he was privileged to be part of an event bringing together his "best friends".The DP used the forum to reiterate that it is good to continue building bridges of unity and peace in the country.